title: Geauga County Juvenile Court wins $290,000 for victim assistance
text:
Geauga County Juvenile Court wins $290,000 for victim assistance 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
The Geauga County Juvenile Court has earned a $290,000 state grant for its Court Appointed Special Advocates for children program....
